      "factId": "hz.web.62746a522e4d4af1.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "They do have one thing in common, though: they both use video (and VideoPress!) to add interactive features that help them connect with readers.</p> <p><a href=\"https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1598\" data-permalink=\"https://videopress.com/2014/10/04/fashion-and-tech/geek-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png\" data-orig-size=\"950,449\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"geek\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=950\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1598\" alt=\"geek\" src=\"https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=1024&#038;h=483\" srcset=\"https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=628 628w, https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=150 150w, https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=300 300w, https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png?w=768 768w, https://videopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/geek1.png 950w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" /></a></p> <p>On <em><a href=\"http://virtualizedgeek.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Virtualized Geek</a></em>, IT expert and blogger Keith Townsend holds court on how organizations can most effectively use emerging technologies to meet their missions and stay ahead of the curve.",
